title: 093: Becoming Anabolic
description: Lifting weights is no guarantee that you will build muscle. Your body will only prioritize muscle growth IF you are anabolic. How do you do this? Sal, Adam & Justin break down 5 different ways for you to put your body in an anabolic state so that it wants to build muscle and lose fat.
